## SEO Requirements (CRITICAL)
- Every page MUST have unique meta title (under 60 chars)
- Every page MUST have unique meta description (under 160 chars)
- Every page MUST have ONE H1 tag only
- Use H2-H6 hierarchy correctly (no skipping levels)
- Implement JSON-LD schema on every page
- All internal links must use Next.js Link component
- Implement canonical URLs
- Create XML sitemap
- Create robots.txt

## Design Guidelines
- Primary Color: Navy Blue (#1a365d) - trust, professionalism
- Secondary Color: Gold (#d69e2e) - luxury, premium
- Accent Color: Desert Sand (#e2d5c3) - Las Vegas desert aesthetic
- Font Family: 
  - Headings: Playfair Display (serif, luxury feel)
  - Body: Inter or Source Sans Pro (clean readability)
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Minimum touch target: 44x44px
- Maximum content width: 1280px
- Section padding: py-16 md:py-24

